      "span_text": "tools (The Chronicle of Higher Education, 2010). To the contrary, a recent study found that 80% of surveyed academics use and maintain social networking sites of certain type. conducted telephone interviews with fifty-seven academics from twenty-eight United States' universities and discovered that all of the participants used social networking tools for personal, academic, professional, or research purposes."
